ðŸ–Œ Text formatting using Minecraft color codes.

## Installation

To install MCFC, run the following command:

```
 pip install mcfc
```

## Preview

![Preview](images/preview.png)

## Usage

```python
 import mcfc

 mcfc.echo("&cH&6e&el&al&bo&d!")
```

